name: Histidinol dehydrogenase, cytosol
rxn_str: h2o_c + histd_c + 2.0 nad_c <=> 3.0 h_c + his__L_c + 2.0 nadh_c

name: Cystathionine b-lyase
rxn_str: cyst__L_c + h2o_c <=> hcys__L_c + nh3_c + h_c + pyr_c

name: L-Isoleucine:NAD+ oxidoreductase(deaminating)
rxn_str: ile__L_c + nad_c + h2o_c <=> 3mop_c + nh3_c + nadh_c + 2.0 h_c

name: L-alanine dehydrogenase
rxn_str: ala__L_c + h2o_c + nad_c <=> h_c + nadh_c + nh3_c + h_c + pyr_c

name: Asparagine synthetase
rxn_str: asp__L_c + atp_c + nh3_c <=> amp_c + asn__L_c + ppi_c

name: Glutamate dehydrogenase (NAD)
rxn_str: glu__L_c + h2o_c + nad_c <=> akg_c + 2.0 h_c + nadh_c + nh3_c

name: PUTA3
rxn_str: glu5sa_c + h2o_c + nad_c <=> glu__L_c + 2.0 h_c + nadh_c

name: Glutamate synthase  NADH2
rxn_str: akg_c + gln__L_c + h_c + nadh_c <=> 2.0 glu__L_c + nad_c

name: L-phenylalanine:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
rxn_str: phe__L_c + h2o_c + nad_c <=> phpyr_c + nh3_c + nadh_c + 2.0 h_c

name: L-valine:NADP+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
rxn_str: val__L_c + nadp_c + h2o_c <=> 3mob_c + nh3_c + nadph_c + 2.0 h_c

name: L leucine dehydrogenase
rxn_str: h2o_c + leu__L_c + nad_c <=> 4mop_c + h_c + nadh_c + nh3_c + h_c

name: Tryptophanase (L-tryptophan)
rxn_str: h2o_c + trp__L_c <=> indole_c + nh3_c + h_c + pyr_c
